"Rebind it later in Settings → Hotkey." = "Wijzig hem later in Instellingen → Sneltoets.";
"Almost there" = "Bijna klaar";
"You're all set" = "Alles is klaar";
"Two quick permissions so Cutling can work the way you'd expect. You can change either later in Settings." = "Twee snelle machtigingen zodat Cutling werkt zoals je verwacht. Je kunt beide later wijzigen in Instellingen.";
"Launch at login" = "Open bij aanmelden";
"Open Cutling automatically when you sign in." = "Open Cutling automatisch wanneer je je aanmeldt.";
"Accessibility access" = "Toegang tot Toegankelijkheid";
"Granted. Cutling can paste directly into other apps." = "Verleend. Cutling kan rechtstreeks in andere apps plakken.";
"Lets Cutling paste a cutling straight into the app you were using." = "Hiermee kan Cutling een cutling rechtstreeks plakken in de app die je gebruikte.";
"Grant" = "Verlenen";
"You can skip Accessibility and grant it later from Settings → Paste." = "Je kunt Toegankelijkheid overslaan en het later verlenen via Instellingen → Plakken.";
